elements.name: Datasource should not process record(s) with invalid citizen attainment date
elements.description:
"""
    Clarified with PO with the following possible scenario:

    (Q) Can DOB & DOD be on the same date?
    (A) Possible if we are ingesting citizens once they are born but we are not. For now, there is no need to implement this check.

    (Q) Can citizen attainment date & DOD be on the same date?
    (A) Possible. For now, there is no need to implement this check.

    (Q) Can citizen attainment date be after DOD?
    (A) Not likely. For now, there is no need to implement this check since they are separate entities.

    Hence, will be excluding the above mention scenario(s).
    """

MHA sends the MHA_BULK_CITIZEN file to Datasource sftp for processing

the error message contains Must be in yyyyMMdd date format

arguments.val: Must be in yyyyMMdd date format
